ECM’s Creditor Astin Capital Registers $179 Claim, CTK Reports

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-05-20T15:16:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/ecm-s-creditor-astin-capital-registers-179-claim-ctk-reports.html
ECM Real Estate Investments AG (ECM) ’s
creditor Astin Capital Management registered a claim worth 3.1
billion koruna ($179.2 million) against the developer, CTK said,
citing the insolvency registry.  The Luxembourg-based developer filed for insolvency this
week in order to reorganize its business and its debt. The
company is in talks with creditors about establishing a
preliminary creditors committee.  Astin represents ECM bondholders and its claim relates to
ECM’s debt, ECM’s head of investors relation Premysl Hubrt said
by phone.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story: James M. Gomez
at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  